  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to develop and test the usability of a computerized symptom
      assessment and management intervention system in a laboratory setting (phase I) and its
      feasibility in a clinical setting in a group randomized trial (phase II).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
